 The only problem with this shirt is that 

00:03:10.159 --> 00:03:14.849
 it is a bit too short. I mean, it's fine if I don't raise my arms, but 

00:03:14.849 --> 00:03:16.649
 if I do .... well .. 

00:03:20.100 --> 00:03:23.964
 My tip number 1 for copying this shirt? Do not cut accidentally 

00:03:23.970 --> 00:03:28.580
 your shirt is too short. Now I didn't really have a choice, but if you are in doubt 

00:03:28.580 --> 00:03:34.000
 along the length of your shirt, add a few extra inches. If it's too long 

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:37.150
 you can just fold it again and hem, but if you cut it too short 

00:03:37.150 --> 00:03:42.159
 you can't go back. But I think I'm going to wear this with a pinafore or dungarees 

00:03:42.159 --> 00:03:47.349
 who will make sure that I am not so bared. So I can wear it often anyway. 

